            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>tom yum paste</strong>, cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1714735932201-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1714735932201-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1714735932201-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1714735932201-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1714735932201-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>tomato wedges </strong>and <strong>sliced mushrooms</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>to the pan with 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[400ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [500ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong>, your <strong>fish sauce</strong>, <strong>lime leaf[ves] </strong>and <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong></p><p>Add a squeeze of <strong>lime juice</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Drain and add your <strong>king prawns</strong> to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until the prawns are cooked through – this is your <strong>creamy king prawn tom yum</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1714736013830-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
