          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1714736013830-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p><p>Serve the <strong>creamy king prawn tom yum </strong>with the <strong>lemongrass rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge </strong>and the <strong>reserved chilli rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
